hh3cTeTunnel.name: hh3cTeTunnel
hh3cTeTunnel.contactinfo: Platform Team Hangzhou H3C Tech. Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.h3c.com Zip:100085
hh3cTeTunnel.description: This MIB contains managed object definitions for the Multiprotocol Label Switching (MPLS) Te Tunnel.

hh3cTeTunnelMaxTunnelIndex.name: hh3cTeTunnelMaxTunnelIndex
hh3cTeTunnelMaxTunnelIndex.description: The max value of tunnel id is permitted configure on the device.

hh3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspTable.name: hh3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspTable
hh3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspTable.description: This table contains information for static-crlsp, and through this to get detail information about this static-crlsp. Only support transit LSR and egress LSR.

hh3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspEntry.name: hh3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspEntry
hh3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspEntry.description: The entry in this table describes static-crlsp information.

hh3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspInLabel.name: hh3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspInLabel
hh3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspInLabel.description: This is unique label value that manualy assigned. Uniquely identifies a static-crlsp. Managers should use this to obtain detail static-crlsp information.

hh3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspName.name: hh3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspName
hh3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspName.description: The unique name assigned to the static-crlsp.

hh3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspStatus.name: hh3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspStatus
hh3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspStatus.description: Indicates the actual status of this static-crlsp, The value must be up when the static-crlsp status is up and the value must be down when the static-crlsp status is down.

hh3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspRole.name: hh3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspRole
hh3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspRole.description: This value indicate the role of this static-crlsp. This value must be transit at transit point of the tunnel, and tail at terminating point of the tunnel.

hh3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspXCPointer.name: hh3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspXCPointer
hh3cTeTunnelStaticCrlspXCPointer.description: This pointer unique identify a row of mplsXCTable. This value should be zeroDotZero when the static-crlsp is down. The mplsXCTable identifies the segments that compose this tunnel, their characteristics, and relationships to each other.

hh3cTeTunnelCoTable.name: hh3cTeTunnelCoTable
hh3cTeTunnelCoTable.description: This table contains information for Co-routed reverse crlsp and infomation of Co-routed bidirectional Tunnel Interface. If hh3cCorouteTunnelLspInstance is zero, to obtain infomation of Co-routed bidirectional Tunnel Interface, otherwise to obtain Co-routed reverse crlsp infomation.

hh3cTeTunnelCoEntry.name: hh3cTeTunnelCoEntry
hh3cTeTunnelCoEntry.description: The entry in this table describes Co-routed infomation of bidirectional Tunnel Interface and reserver lsp information.

hh3cTeTunnelCoIndex.name: hh3cTeTunnelCoIndex
hh3cTeTunnelCoIndex.description: Uniquely identifies a set of tunnel instances between a pair of ingress and egress LSRs that specified at originating point. This value should be equal to the value signaled in the Tunnel Id of the Session object.

hh3cTeTunnelCoLspInstance.name: hh3cTeTunnelCoLspInstance
hh3cTeTunnelCoLspInstance.description: When obtain infomation of Co-routed bidirectional Tunnel Interface, this vlaue should be zero. And this value must be LspID to obtain reverse crlsp information. Values greater than 0, but less than or equal to 65535, should be useless.

hh3cTeTunnelCoIngressLSRId.name: hh3cTeTunnelCoIngressLSRId
hh3cTeTunnelCoIngressLSRId.description: Identity the ingress LSR associated with this tunnel instance. This vlaue is equal to the LsrID of originating endpoint.

hh3cTeTunnelCoEgressLSRId.name: hh3cTeTunnelCoEgressLSRId
hh3cTeTunnelCoEgressLSRId.description: Identity of the egress LSR associated with this tunnel instance. This vlaue is equal to the LsrID of terminating point.

hh3cTeTunnelCoBiMode.name: hh3cTeTunnelCoBiMode
hh3cTeTunnelCoBiMode.description: This vlaue indicated the bidirection mode of tunnel interface. The valuemust be coroutedActive at the originating point of the tunnel and coroutedPassive at the terminating point.

hh3cTeTunnelCoReverseLspInstance.name: hh3cTeTunnelCoReverseLspInstance
hh3cTeTunnelCoReverseLspInstance.description: This value indicated the reverse lsp instance, and should be equal to obverse lsp instance.

hh3cTeTunnelCoReverseLspXCPointer.name: hh3cTeTunnelCoReverseLspXCPointer
hh3cTeTunnelCoReverseLspXCPointer.description: This pointer unique index to mplsXCTable of the reverse lsp. The mplsXCTable identifies the segments that compose this tunnel, their characteristics, and relationships to each other. A value of zeroDotZero indicate that there is no crlsp assigned to this.

hh3cTeTunnelPsTable.name: hh3cTeTunnelPsTable
hh3cTeTunnelPsTable.description: This table defines some objects for managers to obtain TE tunnel Protection Switching group current status information.

hh3cTeTunnelPsEntry.name: hh3cTeTunnelPsEntry
hh3cTeTunnelPsEntry.description: The entry in this table describes TE tunnel Protection Switching group infromation.

hh3cTeTunnelPsIndex.name: hh3cTeTunnelPsIndex
hh3cTeTunnelPsIndex.description: Uniquely identifies a TE tunnel Protection Switching group instance. This value must be equal to the tunnel id of work tunnel instance.

hh3cTeTunnelPsIngressLSRId.name: hh3cTeTunnelPsIngressLSRId
hh3cTeTunnelPsIngressLSRId.description: Identity the ingress LSR associated with work tunnel instance.

hh3cTeTunnelPsEgressLSRId.name: hh3cTeTunnelPsEgressLSRId
hh3cTeTunnelPsEgressLSRId.description: Identity of the egress LSR associated with work tunnel instance.

hh3cTeTunnelPsProtectIndex.name: hh3cTeTunnelPsProtectIndex
hh3cTeTunnelPsProtectIndex.description: Uniquely identifies a TE tunnel Protection Switching group instance. This value must be equal to the tunnel id of TE tunnel Protection Switching group instance.

hh3cTeTunnelPsProtectIngressLSRId.name: hh3cTeTunnelPsProtectIngressLSRId
hh3cTeTunnelPsProtectIngressLSRId.description: Identity the ingress LSR associated with TE tunnel Protection Switching group instance.

hh3cTeTunnelPsProtectEgressLSRId.name: hh3cTeTunnelPsProtectEgressLSRId
hh3cTeTunnelPsProtectEgressLSRId.description: Identity of the egress LSR associated with TE tunnel Protection Switching group instance.

hh3cTeTunnelPsProtectType.name: hh3cTeTunnelPsProtectType
hh3cTeTunnelPsProtectType.description: This value indicated TE tunnel Protection Switching group type. The default value is oneToOne.

hh3cTeTunnelPsRevertiveMode.name: hh3cTeTunnelPsRevertiveMode
hh3cTeTunnelPsRevertiveMode.description: This value indicated protect switch mode. The value must be revertive or nonRevertive, default value is revertive.

hh3cTeTunnelPsWtrTime.name: hh3cTeTunnelPsWtrTime
hh3cTeTunnelPsWtrTime.description: The cycle time that switch to protect tunnel.

hh3cTeTunnelPsHoldOffTime.name: hh3cTeTunnelPsHoldOffTime
hh3cTeTunnelPsHoldOffTime.description: This value is switchback delay time. When detected the work path fault, switch to protect path after this time.

hh3cTeTunnelPsSwitchMode.name: hh3cTeTunnelPsSwitchMode
hh3cTeTunnelPsSwitchMode.description: This value indicated TE tunnel Protection Switching group switch mode.

hh3cTeTunnelPsWorkPathStatus.name: hh3cTeTunnelPsWorkPathStatus
hh3cTeTunnelPsWorkPathStatus.description: This value indicates work path status. none, noDefect, inDefect will be used.

hh3cTeTunnelPsProtectPathStatus.name: hh3cTeTunnelPsProtectPathStatus
hh3cTeTunnelPsProtectPathStatus.description: This value indicates protect path status. none, noDefect, inDefect(3) will be used.

hh3cTeTunnelPsSwitchResult.name: hh3cTeTunnelPsSwitchResult
hh3cTeTunnelPsSwitchResult.description: This value indicated current using path is work path or protect path.

hh3cTeTunnelPsSwitchWtoP.name: hh3cTeTunnelPsSwitchWtoP
hh3cTeTunnelPsSwitchWtoP.description: This notification is generated when protect workgroup switch from work tunnel to protect tunnel.

hh3cTeTunnelPsSwitchPtoW.name: hh3cTeTunnelPsSwitchPtoW
hh3cTeTunnelPsSwitchPtoW.description: This notification is generated when protect workgroup switch from protect tunnel to work tunnel.

hh3cTeTunnelNotificationsGroup.name: hh3cTeTunnelNotificationsGroup
hh3cTeTunnelNotificationsGroup.description: This group contains MPLS Te Tunnel traps.

hh3cTeTunnelScalarsGroup.name: hh3cTeTunnelScalarsGroup
hh3cTeTunnelScalarsGroup.description: Scalar object needed to implement MPLS te tunnels.

hh3cTeTunnelCorouteGroup.name: hh3cTeTunnelCorouteGroup
hh3cTeTunnelCorouteGroup.description: Objects for quering Co-routed reverse crlsp information.

hh3cTeTunnelPsGroup.name: hh3cTeTunnelPsGroup
hh3cTeTunnelPsGroup.description: Objects for quering protect workgroup information.
